user function-Handles login operations

restuarnt function-handles display of avaliable resturants and its selection

def_order_menu-Direct to resturant menu or exit menu based on selection

def_full_file_reader-Handles operation about reading the menu that stores in local system

def_file_sorter-sorting the resturant menu

def_food_drink_order-Displaying no of items in each resturant and handles its selection

def_report-generates report based on each order

def_payment-Handles payment operation   

some of these functions are repeatedly used based on selection of particular resturant
